Sentencas: Co-deposition of CuO and Mn1.5Co1.5O4 by single step electrophoretic deposition is used to produce similar to 15 mm coatings on Crofer22APU steel, which finds use as interconnect for high temperature solid oxide cells.
Titulo: Co-deposition of CuO and Mn1.5Co1.5O4 powders on Crofer22APU by electrophoretic method: Structural, compositional modifications and corrosion properties

Sentencas: Sintering of the green coatings in reducing and then oxidizing conditions led to formation of a mixed (Cu, Mn,Co)(3)O-4 spinel.
Titulo: Co-deposition of CuO and Mn1.5Co1.5O4 powders on Crofer22APU by electrophoretic method: Structural, compositional modifications and corrosion properties

Sentencas: By the incorporation of Cu, the density of the coatings improved.
Titulo: Co-deposition of CuO and Mn1.5Co1.5O4 powders on Crofer22APU by electrophoretic method: Structural, compositional modifications and corrosion properties

Sentencas: Scanning and transmission electron microscopy observations, supplemented with energy dispersive spectroscopy, confirmed dissolution of Cu in the spinel phase.
Titulo: Co-deposition of CuO and Mn1.5Co1.5O4 powders on Crofer22APU by electrophoretic method: Structural, compositional modifications and corrosion properties

Sentencas: For the un-doped Mn1.5Co1.5O4 both the tetragonal and cubic phases are detected at room temperature by X-ray diffractometry, whereas the addition of Cu seems to stabilize the cubic phase.
Titulo: Co-deposition of CuO and Mn1.5Co1.5O4 powders on Crofer22APU by electrophoretic method: Structural, compositional modifications and corrosion properties

Sentencas: Initial ( similar to 1000 h) high temperature corrosion evaluation at 800 degrees C in air showed promising properties of the mixed spinel coating.
Titulo: Co-deposition of CuO and Mn1.5Co1.5O4 powders on Crofer22APU by electrophoretic method: Structural, compositional modifications and corrosion properties
